1st Step : download redis version 3.2.100.zip =>
            link( https://github.com/microsoftarchive/redis/releases/tag/win-3.2.100)
2nd Step : create new folder "Redis" in your windows/C partition
3rd Step : extract the downloaded redis zip files in to your Redis folder
4th Step : run redis-server.exe by clicking inside your Redis folder
5th Step : write those go codes inside go files
6th Step : go run main.go

